title: Mars Lander - Episode 2
description:
Your Mars exploration ship takes you above a particularly rocky area. You will have to review and improve your descent technique in order to land your mars rover safely on martian ground.

Topic: Position, speed and angle regulation.

This medium puzzle is the second in a series of three exercises proposed during the “Mars Lander” past contest. Once solved feel free to try and master the third puzzle “Mars Lander - Level 3” on the same topic but with an increased difficulty!
